loads header of NID file and separates into items first item in list has the titles of the others

read.NID_headerItems(filename)

Arguments

filename

filename including path

Value

list

Examples

filename = system.file("extdata", "NanoSurf_20160301.nid",package="nanoscopeAFM")
read.NID_headerItems(filename)
